sections.Trivia:
- The manga version of this story happens over 3 days. In the manga, the 10th of October falls on a Saturday with Health and Sports Day falling on the 12th. The scene where Kogoro gives Eri her present happens shortly after midnight on the 12th. In the anime version, the 10th falls on a Sunday with the 11th being Health and Sports Day. In this version, the same scene happens shortly after 11:00 PM on the 11th.
- The second part of this episode came out in October 2010. By coincidence, October 10th fell on a Sunday that year.
- The Porsche toy models are a 1995 carrera white Porsche 911 Carrera RS [993] and James Dean's 1955 Porsche 550 Spyder.
- The other toy cars in are a 1970 alpine blue Renault A110 Berlinette 1600 S, a 1972 dark metallic blue Ford Gran Torino, a 1965 Rangoon red Ford Mustang and a 1988 Rosso Corsa Ferrari F40.
- The suspects' names come from "public holidays in Japan"[1]:
Akiho Kokubu (国分 秋穂) and Takehiko Kokubu (国分 建彦) both come from the National Foundation Day (建国記念の日 ,Kenkoku Kinen no Hi?) and the Autumnal Equinox Day (秋分の日 ,Shūbun no Hi?) ;
Midori Hino (日野 緑) comes from Greenery Day (みどりの日 ,Midori no Hi?) ;
Seiji Hino (日野 成治) comes from Coming of Age Day (成人の日 ,Seijin no Hi?).
